race.comment: Tough contest. GRINZINGER NYX (16) snagged back from the wide draw at latest when a below par ninth over 1400m at Echuca. Expected to roll forward from the better gate and represents each way value. DIVAZOU (3) went down narrowly last start when well in the market, finishing second at Corowa over 1400m, beaten only half a length. Can feature. KOTAISHI (5) was out of the placings two back but turned things around more recently, beaten a head when second over 1400m at Nowra. In the mix. TALUK (2) has had a few chances but doesn't win out of turn. Progressed nicely last time out when fifth over 1200m at Wagga. Well placed to give this a shake.
